@NODE introduction "Introduction"
@{u}KewlPage?@{uu}

   This is a door which pages you in a kewl way (hence KewlPage!), with a whole
of features this is the ultimate page door for MAX's BBS systems. This is just
a paging door though and requires a seperate chat door, recommended chat doors
are KewlChat/YaanChat by Niki Murkett (KewlPage is enhanced for YaanChat) or
MaxsChat by Edward Lawford.

@{u}Requirements@{uu}

Kickstart 2.04+
MAX's BBS V1.54 68000 or MAX's Pro.
Memory requirements increase depending on samples, modules, etc used.

@{i}Requirements for optional features: @{ui}
medplayer.library (LIBS:) for MED modules.
narrator.device (DEVS:) & translator.library (LIBS:) for speech.

@ENDNODE


